Use the standard library
This is how to sum_squares of lst:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that n is lst's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      Remember that total is sum of total and (product of x and x)
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is diff of 0 and total
